已知数列{an}的前n项和为Sn,且Sn=2n2+n,n∈N*,数列{bn}满足an=4log2bn+3,n∈N*.(1)求an,bn;(2)求数列{an·bn}的前n项和Tn.答案(1)an=4n-1,n∈N*bn=2n-1,n∈N*(2)Tn=(4n-5)2n+5,n∈N*解析解:(1)由Sn=2n2+n,得当n=1时,a1=S1=3;当n≥2时,an=Sn-Sn-1=4n-1所以an=4n-1,n∈N*由4n-1=an="4"log2bn+3,得bn=2n-1,n∈N*.(2)由(1)知anbn=(4n-1)·2n-1,n∈N*,所以Tn=3+7×2+11×22+…+(4n-1)·2n-1,2Tn=3×2+7×22+…+(4n-5)·2n-1+(4n-1)·2n,所以2Tn-Tn=(4n-1)2n-[3+4(2+22+…+2n-1)]=(4n-5)2n+5故Tn=(4n-5)2n+5,n∈N*.
